# API OpenAPI Requirements

Every `app/controllers/api/` action MUST have matching OpenAPI under `specs/api/` (`openapi.yml`, `paths/`, `schemas/`). If you edit `app/views/api/**/*.jbuilder`, update those specs so the documented JSON matches the response.

Per endpoint: method + path, summary, parameters, request body (if any), responses (200/201, 401, 422, 500), `security: [ bearerAuth: [] ]`, at least one example per response.

**Versioning**: Routes today use `/api` without `/v1` (e.g. `/api/compiles`). For **new** endpoints, prefer `/api/v1/...` and versioned controllers; keep existing paths until a deliberate migration.

Validate before commit: `bundle exec rake openapi:validate`
